{"tid":1682082,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"救下你地推行動 post","createTime":"2019-10-30T00:07:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T02:21:34.000Z","uid":99397,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"210364dcab7713d4384a6c471df0c169aebabcb7","tid":1682082,"uid":99397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T00:07:02.000Z","msg":"仲有好多行動post 需要大家推<br />\n<br />\n〖11月2號行動〗想贏就入黎啊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1681160\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1681160</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今個星期主線任務：1031太子站、112維園<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1679401\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1679401</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【112維園見】全球33個城市響應號召，一句講曬，香港人出唔出先？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1681365\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1681365</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n112 去維園<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1680408\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1680408</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n除左正評留名推post<br />\n你地仲可以開post!！<br />\n上面既post 加加埋埋都幾百個正評<br />\n只要有一半人都開post宣傳<br />\n就算上唔到熱門 都佔左大多數既post!<br />\n達到宣傳作用！<br />\n簡單兩句講下自己一路以黎既感受 呼籲下大家去就得！<br />\n<br />\n11。2！ 3點 維園見！<br />\nBe Water!!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vzw7FwU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVzw7FwU.jpg&h=41ff3cec&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y7nbnLf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy7nbnLf.jpg&h=435aeea9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zaHOpYB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzaHOpYB.jpg&h=8e5c45df&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a31a9b0cde2882231e167f8ad71518aec5082ba0","tid":1682082,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T00:08:11.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，推post &amp; 借個靚位<br />\n<br />\n鐘庭耀教授為今次運動發起了超大型全港民調，追蹤長期民意，做份國際文宣，話比全世界聽， 5毛網軍不代表香港人(眾籌